product_desc: Our vision is to build a jewellery company to be the go to destination to shop for jewellery online. India is one of the leading manufactures of jewellery worldwide but yet today India has only few branded B&M or Online store-fronts leveraging its domestic manufacturing capabilities to sell within India. We want to be the selling portal for manufacturers to come and sell jewellery online through our website providing white label solutions making us the Industry lead and expert in this category.
high_concept: To be online destination for fashion jewelry
name: NIZANTA
